<h2>Return Initiated</h2>
<p>Hello <strong><%= customerName %></strong>,</p>
<p>Your return request has been successfully received and approved. Here are the details:</p>

<div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3>Return Details</h3>
    <p><strong>Order Number:</strong> <%= orderNumber %></p>
    <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= orderId %></p>
    <p><strong>Return Number:</strong> <%= returnNumber %></p>
    <p><strong>Return Initiated Date:</strong> <%= new Date(initiatedDate).toLocaleDateString() %></p>
    <p><strong>Return Reason:</strong> <%= reason || 'Requested by customer' %></p>
    <p><strong>Return Status:</strong> <span style="color: #ffc107; font-weight: bold;">Initiated</span></p>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3>Return Items</h3>
    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <thead>
            <tr style="border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;">
                <th style="text-align: left; padding: 10px;">Product</th>
                <th style="text-align: center; padding: 10px;">Qty</th>
                <th style="text-align: right; padding: 10px;">Return Amount</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <% items.forEach(item => { %>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">
                    <td style="padding: 10px;">
                        <strong><%= item.productName %></strong><br/>
                        <small>Color: <%= item.color %> | Size: <%= item.size %></small>
                    </td>
                    <td style="text-align: center; padding: 10px;"><%= item.quantity %></td>
                    <td style="text-align: right; padding: 10px;">₹<%= parseFloat(item.returnAmount).toFixed(2) %></td>
                </tr>
            <% }); %>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <div style="text-align: right; margin-top: 15px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 2px solid #ddd;">
        <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Total Return Amount:</strong> ₹<%= parseFloat(totalReturnAmount).toFixed(2) %></p>
    </div>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3>Pickup Instructions</h3>
    <p><strong>Pickup Date:</strong> <%= new Date(pickupDate).toLocaleDateString() %></p>
    <p><strong>Pickup Time Window:</strong> <%= pickupTimeWindow || 'Between 10 AM - 4 PM' %></p>
    <p><strong>Pickup Location:</strong> <%= pickupAddress || 'Your registered address' %></p>
    <p><strong>Pickup Agent Contact:</strong> <%= pickupAgentPhone || 'To be updated' %></p>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
    <h3 style="color: #856404; margin-top: 0;">Important Before Return</h3>
    <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #856404;">
        <li>Pack the items in their original packaging if possible</li>
        <li>Include all tags, labels, and original accessories</li>
        <li>Ensure items are clean and in original condition</li>
        <li>Keep your return number handy for the pickup agent</li>
        <li>Ensure someone is available during the pickup window</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="<%= trackingUrl %>" style="background-color: #FF6B6B; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;">Track Return</a>
</div>

<p>Once we receive and verify your return, we'll process the refund within 3-5 business days.</p>
<p>Thank you for giving us the opportunity to make things right!</p>
